message.body: YAY. So how are you buddy? How's school and life and everything?
I'm great. Junior year is very stressful, but it's fun. 3 Aps and a shit ton of extra curriculars. Hows Emory man?
That's good! Hopefully everything you're doing is something you enjoy. Emory is great, I really feel comfortable here and I'm having lots of fun. The work is hard but it's manageable
